      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·005.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">中谷有蓷.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>中谷有蓷，暵其脩矣。有女仳離，條其歗矣。條其歗矣！遇人之不淑矣！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the valleys grows the mother-wort,
But scorched is it where it had become long.
There is a woman forced to leave her husband;
Long-drawn are her groanings!
Long-drawn are her groanings!
She suffers from his misfortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
