      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·王風·005.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">中谷有蓷.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>中谷有蓷，暵其濕矣。有女仳離，啜其泣矣。啜其泣矣！何嗟及矣！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the valleys grows the mother-wort,
But scorched is it even in the moist places.
There is a woman forced to leave her husband;
Ever flow her tears!
Ever flow her tears!
But of what avail is her lament?</seg>
      </tuv>
